videos.title: Winter Loves Punishing Draws
videos.description:
Owling Mine was an old archetype but it's back in standard and with way more efficient draw punishers thanks to Scrawling Trawler and Winter! If you're also a Nekusar commander player, you'll love this!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
